This weekend I am taking extra time to give myself compassion. I hit some setbacks to reaching my goal of running the DC Rock & Roll Marathon this March with a decent finish time.

Since mid-September I’ve been struggling with IT Band Syndrome and about a week before Thanksgiving, I was seeing enough progress with the injury that I decided to officially register for the marathon and make it my victorious return to the sport. But unfortunately it has started to get worse again,
